    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Then what should an angel fight for Zack? What do angels dream of?! Angels dream of one thing... To be human.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You have a single wind sprouting out of your back. Your Dexterity score maximum is increased by 2. You gain a glide speed equal to your movement speed. Additionally, you may use your bonus action to gain a flying speed equal to half your normal movement speed.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>You can not wear heavy armor.</p>",
